ible by default on your profile"> Sui's death is this for his brother Bennu Kagaho</span>.</li></ul></div><p></p><div class="folderlabel" onclick="togglefolder('folder1');">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; D-F&nbsp;</div><div id="folder1" class="folder" isfolder="true" style="display:block;"><ul><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DangerousForbiddenTechnique" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DangerousForbiddenTechnique">Dangerous Forbidden Technique</a>: <span class="spoiler" title="you can set spoilers visible by default on your profile"> Athena Exclamation, <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/AllYourPowersCombined" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/AllYourPowersCombined">Zodiac Clamation</a>.</span></li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DarkAndTroubledPast" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DarkAndTroubledPast">Dark and Troubled Past</a>: Tenma, Manigoldo, Regulus, Yuzuriha, even <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/TheDragon" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/TheDragon">Pandora</a>.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DarkIsEvil" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DarkIsEvil">Dark Is Evil</a>: Hades and his Specters.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DarkSkinnedBlond" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DarkSkinnedBlond">Dark-Skinned Blond</a>: Gemini Deuteros (albeit with blue hair), who originally thought to be because he spent several years in an island wearing little more than a loincloth, was confirmed as the former when childhood flashbacks do show him as a <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DarkSkinnedBlond" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DarkSkinnedBlond">Dark-Skinned Blunette</a> while in the Sanctuary.<ul><li> Cait Sith Cheshire, although with white hair.</li></ul></li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/TheDarkSide" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/TheDarkSide">The Dark Side</a>: Alone. <span class="spoiler" title="you can set 