" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/KilledOffForReal">Killed Off for Real</a>: See <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/KillEmAll" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/KillEmAll">Kill 'Em All</a>.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/KnightInSourArmor" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/KnightInSourArmor">Knight in Sour Armor</a>: Arguably, Alone. <span class="spoiler" title="you can set spoilers visible by default on your profile"> Not Hades, Alone.</span></li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/LightIsNotGood" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/LightIsNotGood">Light Is Not Good</a>: The Lost Canvas itself. It basically depicts a whole lot of angels, which <span class="spoiler" title="you can set spoilers visible by default on your profile">eventually gain a life of their own to block Tenma's attacks in his final confrontation with Alone.</span></li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/LightningBruiser" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/LightningBruiser">Lightning Bruiser</a>: Taurus Rasgado, the fastest Saint.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/LivingOnBorrowedTime" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/LivingOnBorrowedTime">Living on Borrowed Time</a>: <span class="spoiler" title="you can set spoilers visible by default on your profile">Leo Ilias, Scorpio Kardia, Gemini Aspros after his <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/HeelFaceTurn" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/HeelFaceTurn">Heel&#150;Face Turn</a></span>.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/LivingWeapon" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/LivingWeapon">Living Weapon</a> : <span class="spoiler" title="you can set spoilers visible by default on your profile"> Mephistopheles Youma claims Pegasus Tenma is this and that he plans to harvest his soul in order to take down the Olympus Gods</span>.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/LotusEaterMachine" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Lo